{"tid":1733094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如今只能守到入醫院","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T08:32:21.000Z","uid":80972,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"025ee6fcbbcf2daa8dc1d4fcdc7550809f70dad4","tid":1733094,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"1) 對外宣佈，寧願斷糧都死守唔出，對五大訴求係至死方休。用骨風吸引香港社會同國際社會關注，減低血腥鎮壓嘅可能。<br />\n<br />\n2) 死守一黎係拖到出面手足諗到方法，二黎係真係要捱到就死，等各方以人道原因逐個手足送去醫院先。捱唔住就逐個送去A core，逐個個打橫瞓喺度俾傳媒影相，製造輿論，叫泛民/校友/社會人員施壓，俾白車入黎。48個鐘要喺醫院過，至少可以保命。如果d狗賤到等你好返先拉人，at least有record 知你冇傷，如果拉左之後又被打，咁都有個保障，好過冇。"},{"pid":"4f02fa41592d153cdd3b3790cc0c8ae24325b88b","tid":1733094,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ebf253ede0ed2a217dcbef677cab6cc03a25d62","tid":1733094,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c35bfadb8a235fcba20edf26d637e6e6123a67c","tid":1733094,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82e398b26f5238c8f5c9e6a259ca9b485420b38","tid":1733094,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54bbf5a6bd5aa6aaa9d295811f1c4940b415e3b2","tid":1733094,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35a74f9b922f85d06f448077091bae783cb3e9bc","tid":1733094,"uid":43179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 小心風向撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe88147839124b78aa50f96222b5bff116535599","tid":1733094,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"push"